## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of interest group dynamics. Additionally, the influence of interest groups can vary significantly across different political systems and contexts, which this report does not fully explore. The findings are primarily focused on the U.S. political system, limiting the applicability to other countries with different regulatory frameworks and political cultures.